    "app":  "wkappbot-webbot",
    "title":  "ChatGPT BLANK false-positive guard",
    "desc":  "After ChatGPT responds it navigates to /c/UUID, causing transient BLANK detection. Logic: blankCount++; if blankCount \u003e= 3 abort with BLANK_PAGE. No dynamic 30s/20-blank window ??simple 3-strike rule.",
    "steps":  [
                  "PollStreamingResponseAsync polls every 1s",
                  "On \u0027\\x01BLANK\u0027: blankCount++; if \u003e= 3 return (false, \"BLANK_PAGE\")",
                  "Otherwise continue polling until timeoutSec elapsed"
              ],
